steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitdash00201" and Comment "Testing"
When I add new table with Name "jitdash00202" and Comment "Testing"
When I navigate to menu "Dashboard app" without submenu
Then I should see Dashboard screen display
Then I should see table Name "jitdash00201" displayed in dashboard list
Then I should see table Name "jitdash00202" displayed in dashboard list
When I select table Name "jitdash00201" in dashboard table list
When I toggle on switcher of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash00201"
When I click general any span text button label "Select Table Columns" with index "1"
When I click general any span text button label "Select Table Columns" with index "2"
When I select multi dropdown label "Order by" index "1" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash00201" by value "jitdash00201s.created_at"
When I select multi dropdown label "Order by" index "2" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash00201" by value "Asc"
When I select table Name "jitdash00202" in dashboard table list
Then I should see name of table "jitdash00202" displayed in heading
